'''佐伊·伊莎贝拉·克拉维茨'''（{{lang-en|Zoë Isabella Kravitz}}，{{bd|1988年|12月1日|catIdx=Kravitz, Zoe}}）<ref>[http://movies.nytimes.com/person/1465139/Zoe-Kravitz/biography "Zoe Kravitz. Alternate Name: Zoe Isabella Kravitz"] {{Wayback|url=http://movies.nytimes.com/person/1465139/Zoe-Kravitz/biography |date=20131016195240 }} at All Movie Guide via ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]''</ref><ref name=google01>{{Cite news |first=Noreen |last=Seebacher |title=Lisa Bonet has baby |date=December 1, 1988 |url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=6t4cAAAAIBAJ&sjid=fGMEAAAAIBAJ&pg=3614,561849&hl=en |newspaper=[[The_Pittsburgh_Press|The Pittsburgh Press]] |accessdate=June 13, 2010 |archive-date=2022-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220405000724/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=6t4cAAAAIBAJ&sjid=fGMEAAAAIBAJ&pg=3614,561849&hl=en }}</ref>，是一名[[美国|美国]][[女演员|女演员]]、[[歌手|歌手]]和[[模特儿|模特儿]]。她曾参演电影《[[料理絕配|美味情缘]]》(2007)、《[[勇敢復仇人|勇敢復仇人]]》(2007)、和饰演超级英雄电影《[[X战警：第一战|X战警：第一战]]》(2011)中的精靈（Tempest）。她也在《[[加州靡情|加州靡情]]》第四季饰演珍珠，2014年在[[反乌托邦|反乌托邦]]科幻电影《[[分歧者·異類叛逃|分歧者]]》中饰演克里斯蒂娜。

==早年==
克拉维茨出生在美國加利福尼亚州洛杉矶[[威尼斯_(洛杉矶)|威尼斯海滩]]，她是女演员{{tsl|en|Lisa Bonet|莉莎·博内特}}和音乐家[[藍尼·克羅維茲|藍尼·克羅維茲]]的独生女<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.list.co.uk/article/105941-zoe-kravitz-not-restricted-by-race/|title=Zoe Kravitz not restricted by race|accessdate=2019-01-19|date=2018-12-31|work=The List|archive-date=2019-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190119174836/https://www.list.co.uk/article/105941-zoe-kravitz-not-restricted-by-race/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=google01/>。她的祖母{{tsl|en|Roxie Roker|洛克茜·罗克}}是非洲裔美国女演员，有巴哈马血统<ref>{{cite web|first=Rhik|last=Samadder|url=https://www.theguardian.com/lifeandstyle/2014/sep/20/lenny-kravitz-this-much-i-know|script-title=en:Lenny Kravitz: ‘I don’t see myself as cool. Generally I’m goofy and ridiculous’|work=The Guardian|date=September 20, 2014|accessdate=May 21, 2018|archive-date=2018-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180521191641/https://www.theguardian.com/lifeandstyle/2014/sep/20/lenny-kravitz-this-much-i-know|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.newsweek.com/crossing-over-143567|title=Crossing Over|accessdate=2019-01-20|date=2002-01-09|last=Samuels|first=Allison|work=Newsweek|archive-date=2019-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190119230830/https://www.newsweek.com/crossing-over-143567|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她的外祖父艾伦·博内特（Allen Bonet）是非洲裔美国人<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{cite web|first=Tish|last=Weinstock|url=https://i-d.vice.com/en_uk/article/gygexj/zoe-kravitz-discusses-the-politics-of-fame-and-racism-in-hollywood|title=zoe kravitz discusses the politics of fame and racism in hollywood|work=i-D magazine|date=April 8, 2016|accessdate=May 8, 2018|archive-date=2018-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180508185239/https://i-d.vice.com/en_uk/article/gygexj/zoe-kravitz-discusses-the-politics-of-fame-and-racism-in-hollywood|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她的祖父[[國家廣播公司|NBC]]新聞電視製作人西·克拉维茨（Sy Kravitz）和外祖母艾琳·利特曼（Arlene Litman）都是[[犹太人|犹太人]]<ref>{{cite web|first=Joy|last=D'Souza|url=https://www.huffingtonpost.ca/2017/05/16/zoe-kravitz-mixed-background_n_16641120.html|title=Zoe Kravitz Reveals How She Learned To Love Her Mixed Background|work=HuffPost Canada|date=May 16, 2017|accessdate=May 8, 2018|archive-date=2019-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190322171950/https://www.huffingtonpost.ca/2017/05/16/zoe-kravitz-mixed-background_n_16641120.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{cite web|first=Henry|last=Barnes|url=https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2015/aug/20/zoe-kravitz-why-do-stories-happen-to-white-people-and-everyone-else-is-a-punchline|script-title=en:Zoë Kravitz: ‘Why do stories happen to white people and everyone else is a punchline?’|work=The Guardian|date=August 20, 2015|accessdate=May 8, 2018|archive-date=2018-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180525153056/https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2015/aug/20/zoe-kravitz-why-do-stories-happen-to-white-people-and-everyone-else-is-a-punchline|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/features/lenny-kravitz-mr-love-58889.html|title=Lenny Kravitz: Mr Love|work=The Independent|date=May 7, 2004|accessdate=May 8, 2018|archive-date=2018-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180508124810/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/features/lenny-kravitz-mr-love-58889.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Jane|last=Mulkerrins|url=https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2017/feb/28/zoe-kravitz-hollywood-race-problem-big-little-lies|title=Zoë Kravitz: 'You're just supposed to assume a character in a script is Caucasian'|work=The Guardian|date=February 28, 2017|accessdate=May 8, 2018|archive-date=2018-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180508185142/https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2017/feb/28/zoe-kravitz-hollywood-race-problem-big-little-lies|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.jpost.com/LifeStyle/Top-10-Hollywood-Jews-you-may-not-have-guessed-327064|title=Top 10 Hollywood: Jews you may not have guessed|author=|date=September 25, 2013|work=|newspaper=The Jerusalem Post - JPost.com|accessdate=May 20, 2018|archive-date=2018-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180217065938/http://www.jpost.com/LifeStyle/Top-10-Hollywood-Jews-you-may-not-have-guessed-327064|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但是她自稱是世俗猶太人<ref>[https://www.rollingstone.com/music/pictures/the-hottest-breakout-stars-of-2011-20110308/hot-progeny-zoe-kravitz-99-357 "Kravitz at Rolling Stone's The Hottest Breakout Stars of 2011"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/pictures/the-hottest-breakout-stars-of-2011-20110308/hot-progeny-zoe-kravitz-99-357 |date=20180521021520 }} Rolling Stone</ref>。

克拉维茨的父母在1987年结婚，6年后（1993年）在她五岁时两人离婚<ref>{{Cite news |first=Emer |last=O'Kelly |title=Lisa returns to the screen from a different world |date=May 21, 2000 |newspaper=[[Irish_Independent|Irish Independent]] |url=http://www.independent.ie/entertainment/arts/lisa-returns-to-the-screen-from-a-different-world-514346.html |accessdate=June 13, 2010 |archive-date=2012-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024033056/http://www.independent.ie/entertainment/arts/lisa-returns-to-the-screen-from-a-different-world-514346.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她和她母亲住到11岁，然后和父亲住在一起，只在夏天和母亲同住。她在迈阿密国家中学（Miami Country Day School）读完学业后，进入纽约曼哈顿的[[华德福教育|鲁道夫·斯坦纳学校]]（Rudolf Steiner School），2007年毕业。此后在{{tsl|en|State University of New York at Purchase|紐約州立大學帕切斯分校}}开始学习表演<ref>{{Cite news |first=Valerie |last=Nome |title=Zoe Kravitz opens up about family, college life |date=September 15, 2007 |magazine=[[OK!|OK!]] |url=http://www.okmagazine.com/2007/09/zoe-kravitz-opens-up-about-family-college-life-1337/ |accessdate=June 14, 2010 }}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。离开大学一年后，她搬到了[[布鲁克林|布鲁克林]]，进入影坛<ref>{{Cite news |first=Frank |last=Lovece |title=Talking to Zoe Kravitz  |date=June 5, 2011 |newspaper=[[Miami_Herald|Miami Herald]] |url=http://www.miamiherald.com/2011/06/05/2250742/talking-to-zoe-kravitz.html |accessdate=June 5, 2011 }}</ref>。

