==私人生活==
克拉维茨有一个同母妹妹(生于2007年7月)和一个同母弟弟(生于2008年12月)，她母亲与演员[[傑森·摩莫亞|傑森·摩莫亞]]（Jason Momoa）結婚。
2009年克拉维茨加入纽约/费城的“电梯战斗”（Elevator Fight）乐队，参加了6月费城的西南偏南音乐节。<ref>{{Cite news|last=Johnson |first=James |date=June 6, 2009 |url=http://www.philly.com/philly/entertainment/20090606_Music__Music_this_week.html |title=Music: Music this week |newspaper=[[Philadelphia_Daily_News|Philadelphia Daily News]] |accessdate=June 7, 2009 }} {{Dead link|date=October 2010|bot=H3llBot}}</ref>

克拉维茨的前男友是《[[X战警：第一战|X战警：第一战]]》中的演员[[迈克尔·法斯宾德|迈克尔·法斯宾德]]，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/x-mens-zoe-kravitz-michael-fassbender-take-relationship-public-201116|title=X-Men Costars Zoe Kravitz, Michael Fassbender Take Relationship Public|work=U.S Magazine|date=June 1, 2011|accessdate=October 6, 2012|archive-date=2014-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140406223203/http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/x-mens-zoe-kravitz-michael-fassbender-take-relationship-public-201116|dead-url=no}}</ref>分手后与《[[花邊教主|绯闻少女]]》演员[[潘·巴奇利|潘·巴奇利]]在2011年年中开始约会，在布鲁克林的威廉斯堡的一个顶楼同居，两人于2013年分手。<ref>{{cite news |date=May 1, 2013 |title=Penn Badgley now living with Zoe Kravitz in perfect pad |url=http://www.10news.com/entertainment/celebrity/penn-badgley-now-living-with-zoe-kravitz-in-perfect-pad_37681535 |publisher=[[10News|10News]] |accessdate=June 17, 2013 |archive-date=2013-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131113170842/http://www.10news.com/entertainment/celebrity/penn-badgley-now-living-with-zoe-kravitz-in-perfect-pad_37681535 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Johnson |first=Zac |date=June 11, 2013 |title=Penn Badgley and Zoe Kravitz Split |url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/penn-badgley-and-zoe-kravitz-split-2013116 |work=US Weekly |accessdate=June 16, 2013 |archive-date=2014-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140214150043/http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/penn-badgley-and-zoe-kravitz-split-2013116 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

